Of course, I'm open to requests.
That's right.

07:39.266 --> 07:43.069
All you got to do is call me, any time.

07:43.103 --> 07:44.604
All right?

07:44.638 --> 07:46.472
Uh... bye.

07:46.506 --> 07:48.007
Call me.

07:48.041 --> 07:49.742
[Gasps] Oh. Boundaries, Mrs. Nguyen.

07:49.776 --> 07:51.310
Boundaries.

07:51.345 --> 07:53.746
MRS. NGUYEN: Why are you here?
You lose that job already?

07:53.780 --> 07:55.281
I should be so lucky.

07:55.315 --> 07:56.983
You don't like your job?

07:57.017 --> 07:58.584
Boo-hoo. Poor baby.

07:58.619 --> 08:01.320
You know, some people work for a living.

08:01.355 --> 08:03.322
No one gives <i>us</i> free cars.

08:03.357 --> 08:05.658
- So why are you here?
- This place is paid up.

08:05.692 --> 08:07.827
I'm within my rights as your legal tenant.

08:07.861 --> 08:09.362
That's all you need to know.

08:09.396 --> 08:12.265
Do I smell coffee? Have you got a pot on?

08:12.299 --> 08:13.699
Why?

08:13.734 --> 08:15.301
[Sighs] How about a fill-up?

08:15.335 --> 08:17.470
You can afford to buy your own.

08:17.504 --> 08:20.373
Faster I get coffee,
the faster I'm out of here.

08:22.976 --> 08:27.647
