[Engine starts]

09:07.754 --> 09:10.122
[Telephones ring in background]

09:23.970 --> 09:26.238
- You haven't unpacked yet?
- Uh...

09:26.273 --> 09:28.541
Kevin and Paige are here.

09:28.575 --> 09:30.376
Absolutely.

09:36.450 --> 09:40.219
[Indistinct office conversations]

09:58.338 --> 10:00.139
I don't know exactly
what Chuck may have said to you,

10:00.173 --> 10:01.440
but just so you know,

10:01.475 --> 10:04.076
I did not ask him to step in on my behalf.

10:04.111 --> 10:06.345
[Indistinct office conversations continue]

10:23.630 --> 10:25.798
Hi, guys. Sorry for the wait.

10:25.832 --> 10:27.400
- Not a problem.
- Hi.

10:27.434 --> 10:29.068
Wonderful to see you again.

10:29.102 --> 10:30.302
- Howard.
- Kevin.

10:30.337 --> 10:32.104
- Hi, Kim.
- Good to see you two.

10:32.139 --> 10:34.440
- Hi, Paige. Hi, Kevin.
- Kim, great to see you.

10:34.474 --> 10:36.242
- Please, have a seat.
- Thank you.

10:36.276 --> 10:37.810
Kevin, how's your grandson?

10:37.844 --> 10:39.178
Oh, outta control,

10:39.212 --> 10:41.347
just running circles around all of us.

10:45.852 --> 10:48.354
[Brakes squeal]

10:48.388 --> 10:49.555
