11:13.480 --> 11:15.514
[Vehicles passing in distance]

11:21.354 --> 11:23.355
[Car door creaks]

11:38.371 --> 11:39.672
[Sighs]

11:39.706 --> 11:43.909
Hello. Can I help you?

11:43.944 --> 11:45.711
You know why I'm here?

11:47.347 --> 11:49.381
He needs an answer.

11:49.416 --> 11:51.917
[Inhales deeply]

11:55.355 --> 11:58.858
Respectfully, I'm gonna have to say no.

12:02.929 --> 12:05.197
You sure about that?

12:05.232 --> 12:06.866
I am.

